    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, grate the <strong>cheddar</strong></p>\r\n<p>Peel and finely chop the <strong>garlic</strong></p>\r\n<p>Combine the <strong>panko breadcrumbs</strong> with <span class=\"text-highlight\">the&nbsp;<strong>chopped garlic, dried oregano,&nbsp;</strong></span><span class=\"text-highlight\">half the</span><span class=\"text-highlight\"><strong> grated cheese&nbsp;</strong>and a </span>generous pinch of<strong> black pepper </strong>&ndash;<strong>&nbsp;</strong>this is your<strong> cheesy crumb</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
