            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the <strong>onion</strong> has softened, stir through the <strong>cooked tortiglioni,</strong>&nbsp;<strong>cr&egrave;me<span class=\"text-highlight\"> fra&icirc;che</span></strong>, <strong>remaining&nbsp;grated cheese</strong> and reserved <strong>starchy pasta water<br /></strong><br />Season with a generous pinch of <strong>black pepper</strong> and cook for 1 min or until the <strong>cheese</strong> has melted</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
